  Experience the addictive gameplay of old-school arcade favourites, updated
  and improved for the 21st century!

  Unique retro-futuristic sound and graphics, player responsive difficulty,
  and a subtle system of tactics combined with classic gameplay make Ultratron
  a fun and hypnotic arcade blast.

  The last human has been slain by evil killer robots. You are the one
  remaining humanoid battle droid. Your mission: avenge the human race! Boost
  your battledroid with powerups, buy cute but deadly pets in the shop. Blast
  your way through 40+ glowing neon levels, avoiding Chasers, Turrets,
  Spawners, Minelayers, bombs, and bullets, and take on the four giant boss
  'bots of the Apocalypse - Ieiunitas, Bellum, Lues and Letum!
